c;">  true</a>: Every bad thing that a public company does, and every bad t=
hing that happens to a public company, is also securities fraud.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The general form of this is something bad happ=
ens and the company does not immediately disclose it, or has not adequately=
 warned shareholders of the risk of it happening, or both. Later, when the =
bad news comes out, the company=E2=80=99s stock drops. Shareholders who bou=
ght the stock before the news came out sue, saying that they were deceived =
about the bad thing and lost money. The US Securities and Exchange Commissi=
on also takes an interest in fraud and might bring an enforcement action.</=
p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Take computer hacking, for instance.=C2=A0If a=
 company gets hacked, that is bad: The hack might disrupt its business, it =
might have to pay a ransom to unlock its files, its customers might stop tr=
usting it, it might get in trouble with regulators for losing customer data=
, etc. If a company gets hacked and does not immediately disclose it, and t=
hen later discloses it and the stock drops, <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bl=
oombergbusiness.com/click/33394198.256419/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvb=
S9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjEtMDItMDMvZ29sZG1hbi1zYWNocy1nb2VzLXRvLXN1cHJl=
bWUtY291cnQtaGVkZ2UtZnVuZHMtd29uLW9uLWdhbWVzdG9wLWtrcG9lNndzP2NtcGlkPUJCRDE=
xMTYyM19NT05FWVNUVUZGJnV0bV9tZWRpdW09ZW1haWwmdXRtX3NvdXJjZT1uZXdzbGV0dGVyJn=
V0bV90ZXJtPTIzMTExNiZ1dG1fY2FtcGFpZ249bW9uZXlzdHVmZg/607f07ceef4b8524a319a2=
3cCac552399" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blan=
k" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom=
-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; back=
ground-color: #ccc;">  it will get sued for securities fraud</a>. (Even if =
it does immediately disclose it, it might get sued for not previously=C2=A0=
warning shareholders about the risk of being hacked, or <a href=3D"https://=
link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/33394198.256419/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb=
21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMTAtMzEvYmFkLXBhc3N3b3Jkcy1hcmUt=
