s like</a> =E2=80=9Cwe use strong passwords=E2=80=9D if, in fact, it did no=
t.)</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Actually hacking is a special case, because ge=
tting hacked is=C2=A0<em>so=C2=A0</em>=C2=A0securities fraud that the SEC r=
ecently <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/33394198.2=
56419/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2VjLmdvdi9uZXdzL3ByZXNzLXJlbGVhc2UvMjAyMy0xMzk/607f0=
7ceef4b8524a319a23cB60f38b75" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope=
" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !importa=
nt; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-s=
tyle: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> wrote new rules about hacking disclo=
sure</a>. These rules, which go into effect next month,=C2=A0require public=
 companies to disclose =E2=80=9Cany cybersecurity incident they determine t=
o be material=E2=80=9D=C2=A0within four days after they decide that it is m=
aterial.=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">One corollary of =E2=80=9Ceverything is securi=
ties fraud=E2=80=9D=C2=A0=E2=80=94=C2=A0and this is the farthest possible t=
hing from legal advice but here we are =E2=80=94=C2=A0one corollary of this=
 is that, if <em>you=C2=A0do=C2=A0</em>a bad thing to a public company, onc=
e you have finished doing the bad thing, there is a fascinating window in w=
hich:</p>
<ol style=3D"list-style-type: decimal; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;"=
>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">You know about the bad thing, because=
 you did it.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">The company knows abo=
ut the bad thing, because it experienced it, and/or because you sent it=C2=
=A0an email like =E2=80=9Cnyah nyah I just hacked your computers.=E2=80=9D<=
/li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">The public does=C2=A0<em>not=C2=A0=
</em>know about the bad thing, because the company has not yet disclosed it=
.</li>
</ol>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">By the theory of =E2=80=9Ceverything is securi=
ties fraud,=E2=80=9D=C2=A0the company is committing securities fraud during=
 this window. (Particularly if the bad thing was a hack and the window has =
been more than four days.)=C2=A0And you know it. How can you take advantage=
?</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">One thing that you could do is short the compa=
ny=E2=80=99s stock, hoping to profit when the bad thing is disclosed. This =
is a well-established approach, but has the problem of being illegal. It is=
 (probably) insider trading: You have material nonpublic information about =
the company, and are trading on it.<a class=3D"footnote-index" href=3D"#foo=
tnote-1" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-=
bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: none =
!important; background-color: transparent !important; display: inline-block=
;">
<span>[1]</span>
</a>=C2=A0You might not care: If you did an <em>illegal=C2=A0</em>bad thing=
 to the company (like hacking), also doing insider trading might not bother=
 you. Still it adds some risk. My <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbus=
iness.com/click/33394198.256419/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9=
uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMTctMDQtMjEvanVpY2UtaGFja2luZy1hbmQtbW9ydGdhZ2UtdGVjaD9jbX=
BpZD1CQkQxMTE2MjNfTU9ORVlTVFVGRiZ1dG1fbWVkaXVtPWVtYWlsJnV0bV9zb3VyY2U9bmV3c=
2xldHRlciZ1dG1fdGVybT0yMzExMTYmdXRtX2NhbXBhaWduPW1vbmV5c3R1ZmY/607f07ceef4b=
8524a319a23cB63622b33" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" targe=
t=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; bor=
der-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: s=
olid; background-color: #ccc;">  Fifth Law of Insider Trading</a> is =E2=80=
=9Cdon=E2=80=99t insider trade by planting bombs at a company and buying pu=
t options on its stock.=E2=80=9D</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Another thing you could do is sue the company =
for securities fraud, but that takes a lot of time and effort. Also you won=
=E2=80=99t get that much money for it unless you owned a lot of the company=
=E2=80=99s stock, and presumably you didn=E2=80=99t. (If you did, why did y=
ou do the bad thing to the company?)</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">A third thing you could do is file a whistlebl=
ower complaint with the US Securities and Exchange Commission saying =E2=80=
=9Chey FYI this company is doing securities fraud.=E2=80=9D And then maybe =
the SEC will investigate and agree and fine the company a pile of money and=
 give you a cut of the money as a whistleblower reward. The SEC does the wo=
rk for you and just hands you the money at the end. Efficient!</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Anyway here is maybe <a href=3D"https://link.m=
ail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/33394198.256419/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxlZXBpbmd=
jb21wdXRlci5jb20vbmV3cy9zZWN1cml0eS9yYW5zb213YXJlLWdhbmctZmlsZXMtc2VjLWNvbX=
BsYWludC1vdmVyLXZpY3RpbXMtdW5kaXNjbG9zZWQtYnJlYWNoLw/607f07ceef4b8524a319a2=
3cBebbfee1b" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blan=
k" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom=
-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; back=
ground-color: #ccc;"> the most Money Stuff story I=E2=80=99ve ever written =
about</a>:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The ALPHV/BlackCat ransomware operation has ta=
ken extortion to a new level by filing a U.S. Securities and Exchange Commi=
ssion complaint against one of their alleged victims for not complying with=
 the four-day rule to disclose a cyberattack.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Earlier today, the threat actor listed the sof=
tware company MeridianLink on their data leak with a threat that they would=
 leak allegedly stolen data unless a ransom is paid in 24 hours.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">LOVE IT. Apparently AlphV hacked into Meridian=
Link=E2=80=99s computers on Nov. 7; <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergb=
usiness.com/click/33394198.256419/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZGF0YWJyZWFjaGVzLm5ldC9hb=
HBodi1maWxlcy1hbi1zZWMtY29tcGxhaW50LWFnYWluc3QtbWVyaWRpYW5saW5rLWZvci1ub3Qt=
