olor: #ccc;"> DataBreaches.net says</a> that =E2=80=9Cthey did not encrypt =
any files, but did exfiltrate files.=E2=80=9D And then they asked MeridianL=
ink for a ransom payment, threatening to release the information they had o=
btained unless they got paid. And then apparently MeridianLink did not pay =
them=C2=A0<em>or=C2=A0</em>publicly disclose the hack, so AlphV went to <a =
href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/33394198.256419/aHR0c=
