emscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decor=
ation: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000=
000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">prior SEC guidanc=
e</a>=C2=A0and the SEC probably already thinks that not promptly disclosing=
 a hack is securities fraud.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Merid=
ianLink <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/33394198.2=
56419/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZGF0YWJyZWFjaGVzLm5ldC9hbHBodi1maWxlcy1hbi1zZWMtY29tc=
GxhaW50LWFnYWluc3QtbWVyaWRpYW5saW5rLWZvci1ub3QtZGlzY2xvc2luZy1hLWJyZWFjaC10=
by10aGUtc2VjLw/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cC97b1d85f" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" it=
emscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decor=
ation: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000=
000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> told DataBreache=
s</a> that =E2=80=9Cbased on our investigation to date, we have identified =
no evidence of unauthorized access to our production platforms, and the inc=
ident has caused minimal business interruption.=E2=80=9D It=E2=80=99s entir=
ely possible that this hack was=C2=A0<em>not=C2=A0</em>material, which is w=
hy MeridianLink neither disclosed it nor paid up.=C2=A0</li>=09<li style=3D=
"margin-bottom: 5px;">Look come on they are obviously not getting a whistle=
blower award even if they are right! They did the hack! This is not really =
a=C2=A0play for money, this is just some combination of (1) attention-seeki=
ng prank (it worked!) and (2) another way to annoy MeridianLink, another th=
reat, a way=C2=A0to extort this victim and future victims into paying up pr=
omptly.</li>
</ol>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Do you think they read Money Stuff? I=C2=A0fee=
l like I have done a lot to popularize the idea that everything is securiti=
es fraud =E2=80=94=C2=A0not as much as the SEC, but a lot =E2=80=94=C2=A0an=
d it is nice to see how far the idea has traveled.</p>
