e=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">I want to call the entity =E2=80=9CDon=E2=80=99t =
Touch My Money.=E2=80=9D</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">But if I =
do that, eventually someone will notice and get suspicious and it will look=
 bad at my fraud trial.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">So I will =
call it DTMM instead, just a neutral string of letters; <em>I </em>will kno=
w what it means, but no one can prove it.</li>
</ol>
